{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act22side", "eventName": "照我以火", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "FC-7", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "生靈火花", "storyInfo": "從戰場逃離後，風笛的情緒終於爆發，她質問葦草小丘郡事件的真相，以及有關深池的一切。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g4_swamp_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "volume": 0.9, "loop": "true", "channel": "walksp"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "walksp", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等一等，阿赫茉妮。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "前方公路關卡的駐軍數量有些異常。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您注意到了？我恰好還告訴過他們留意......這裡也許會發生一些破壞公爵間關係的事件。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......所以你必須趕在那些人離開特倫特郡轄區之前動手圍捕，這樣你留的後手才能夠起效。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#6$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不算意外。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......威靈頓公爵手下，赤鐵近衛隊的長官，當然，這個身份很快就威脅不到您了。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，您至少很清楚，繼續追擊下去，事情會變成兩位大公爵的領地爭端。在當前維多利亞的局勢下，恐怕沒人想看到這樣的衝突發生。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#8$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，為什麼你總是不給我留一些選擇餘地呢？", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，現在這樣也夠了，我的任務也已經完成了。", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的失誤造成了這樣的惡果。作為身份已經暴露的間諜，你沒有必要再如此盡職地虛張聲勢。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？我可是真心希望，我們能共同為有朝一日的合作付出努力——", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿赫茉妮。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在台上說的話已經夠多了。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#5$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#3"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳......", "name": "阿赫茉妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_228_1#3"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人，收隊。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這原本就是一場敗仗，先放過他們。", "name": "“校官”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_723_1#1$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "volume": 0.9, "loop": "true", "channel": "walksp1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "walksp1", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_228_1#3"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "volume": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "ahmnwalk"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "ahmnwalk", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我提醒過你，菲舍爾。礦石病發展到一定程度之後，這些止痛藥就不管用了。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在的情況，就是你長時間持續使用源石技藝的後果。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我當然知道。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好吧，如果我話說得太重，我道歉。", "name": "特別行動隊隊長"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我只是在想......", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#6$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_399_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尊敬的開斯特公爵竟然派來了一位“灰禮帽”。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我甚至不知道......那位公爵的密使是什麼時候取代了我的人。", "name": "菲舍爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_4017_puzzle_1#1$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g4_swamp_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......哈......我們，我們是不是逃出來了？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#5$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，後面看不到追兵了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先停下來檢查一下受傷的情況吧，及時處理。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們......失去了幾名夥伴。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在這裡等等吧，煙霧裡有人被衝散了，也許還躲在樹林裡。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前你跟他們說好的前進方向是這邊，如果他們還記得，應該會找過來。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我們只稍微停留一會。天就要亮了，我不會耽誤你們的行程。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "其他人也可以放下武器，暫時休息......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......風笛？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i06", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 200.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "duration": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$distressed_intro", "key": "$distressed_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“葦草”。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你就是小丘郡的那個術師。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你就是那場火的操縱者。我認識你的法術，你讓整條街道變成了灰燼。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你讓Outcast為救你而死。", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你就是深池的“領袖”，是嗎？", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人全都在看著她，在等一個回答。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個問題，她從過去到現在聽過許多次。每次聽到的時候，她都需要拼命遏制自己搖頭的欲望。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i02", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可她想起了乾草垛的觸感和晚風的味道。"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i01", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想起帳篷前躍動的篝火，和槍尖上的火截然不同。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_coldforest", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_closeeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想起遠處還未完全消散的濃煙，那一聲聲呼喊彷彿仍有回聲。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "這一次，她不再想搖頭。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "34_i06", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 0.85, "yScaleTo": 0.85, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 4.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在小丘郡的時候，我想以死永遠擺脫我的身份，所以源石炮彈落下時我沒有躲開。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島救起我之後，我試圖為自己的命運扳回什麼，所以我踏上這趟旅程，試圖撫平一些深池的暴力留下的傷痕。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "葦草", "content": "但此刻，對於你的這個問題，我只會回答，"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "葦草", "content": "我是。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g4_swamp_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些死去的人......因深池而死的人。“塔拉人”。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深池......欺騙他們了，不是嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......過去我會說，那些人的生命，不過是深池之火的燃料。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了大局，為了全體塔拉人能起身反抗身上的不公，這把火必須燒得很旺很旺。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那些話......在我被Outcast救下，在我重新走過這些路之後，我沒有辦法再說出口。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實際上，總有一些死亡，原本是可以避免的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能說，所有的死難者，他們都是為深池的大業而犧牲的......塔拉人是一個又一個活著的，活生生的人。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記得深池犯的錯......尤其是我親手犯下的那些。我不會去掩蓋這些醜陋的傷痕。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有......“赤鐵近衛隊”。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今晚想帶走你的深池士兵，是威靈頓公爵的人。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們......是公爵的私兵？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，深池的背後並沒有......也不該有任何勢力。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果有，那就是......所有想要安寧的家鄉，想在自己的土地上自由行走的塔拉人。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是你很怕深池。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是深池真的如你所說，是為了保護塔拉人而戰，那你在害怕什麼？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在怕......什麼？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想像中的深池很好，可是實際上裡面全都是暴徒、陰謀家、你控制不了的人。你甚至都被他們扔在了外面，不是嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會否認，許多人在深池的火光裡，看到的不是塔拉人的道路，只是自己的未來。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想......維多利亞人一磚一石地壘砌自己的家園時，也不會想起，自己在為維多利亞而付出。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只不過，維多利亞人已經有他們的家園和土地了，可以平靜地建造、耕耘。塔拉人想要活著，卻要流很多血。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想看見任何人流血。是的，我很害怕，害怕流血，害怕死亡......所以我總想著躲起來。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不去思考，不去感受，就像一個......影子。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是這樣就可以了嗎？為什麼在我看不見的地方，血......還在流？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "葦草......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......風笛。你們之前總是問我，要帶著這些塔拉人往哪裡走。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我問你，深池的夢想是不能實現的嗎？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風笛很少覺得失望。"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想過自己的報告書永遠交不到正確的人手裡，也想過自己的戰友們是在預謀已久的爭端中無謂地犧牲。"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她想過自己再次面對深池的時候要如何瓦解他們的陰謀，從他們手中保護無辜的平民百姓。"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在，她看到了小丘郡事件背後只是公爵之間的彼此試探，也看到了葦草身後那幾個從戰火中走出來的塔拉人迷茫又驚惶的眼睛。"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說不上來自己在對誰失望。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不知道自己還能從葦草口中得到什麼答案，就如她同樣回答不了葦草的問題。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......該走了，陳。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的任務是調查深池的真相。現在，我聽深池“領袖”親口說清楚了。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，葦草幹員聽起來暫時不會跟著我們回羅德島。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她還有自己的事要做，我們也有我們的。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "volume": 0.7, "loop": "true", "channel": "walksp2"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "walksp2", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowsrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風、風笛！", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......維恩？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個......送給你。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收音機？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們之後還要在荒野上趕路吧？拿著這個收音機，說不定能聽到什麼有用的消息......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不需要它了嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......哈哈，關於塔拉人的消息，不總是翻來覆去那幾樣嗎？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "風笛，我們真的很感謝你，感謝陳，感謝那個......羅德島。謝謝你們的帳篷和這一路上的幫助。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有......再見。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "再見，維恩。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.3}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老舊的收音機在風笛手中發出一陣嗞嗞聲。她下意識地放輕了手上的力道。"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保重。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g3_swamp_d", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$loneliness_intro", "key": "$loneliness_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......凱莉，費加爾，你和我。我們現在就剩下這八個人了。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人少一些，倒是容易跑路，哈哈......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......請幫我找一下，手提箱裡還有沒有乾淨的紗布。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "維恩", "content": "唉，好......"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cardboard", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "維恩", "content": "來。"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在我要把傷口附近的布料揭開，會很疼......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_242", "name2": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "shake", "power": 10.0, "times": 100.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶......", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......欸，維恩，你沒那麼怕血了？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？是、是這麼回事......見了這麼多，怕也沒辦法呀。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，葦草......風笛真的就這麼走啦？你們不是朋友嗎？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......也許，以後有一天還會是，但眼下不可能了。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......唉，好吧。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就是覺得，雖然她們本來也要走，可是你和她們應該好好告別的。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人......都應該有一聲道別的。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——欸，莫蘭！", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.2}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_shallowswalk", "volume": 0.7, "loop": "true", "channel": "walksp3"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "walksp3", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們看見莫蘭借著黎明的微光，一瘸一拐地從遠處走來。"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的手裡緊緊地攥著一把斷掉的劍，還有一條沾滿鮮血的頭巾。"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是......塞爾蒙的？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......莫蘭，她最後......怎麼了？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（沉默地搖頭）", "name": "莫蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_728_1#4$1"}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......抱歉，你應該沒能看見。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 334, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "yFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 0.0, "duration": 10.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "遠處的叢林間，戰火燃燒過後的餘煙還在緩緩地升向天空。"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和塞爾蒙一樣，沒有回來的人正躺在那片樹林裡。誰都沒來得及看到，他們最後是什麼樣子。"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倖存者們沉默地注視著飄散的煙。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......他們所有人，都只是......不知去向。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在石高原野，在小丘郡，在橡林郡......", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看過許多場大火。在不同的地方，有人謀劃戰爭與災禍，爭奪權力與聲名。"}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她看著普通人在其中掙扎，又無緣無故地死去。"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她抬起手，德拉克的火焰生出一朵小小的花。"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "握著火焰的感覺依然讓她顫抖，讓她的臟腑疼痛不已，但她卻不再閉上眼睛。"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "BackgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 0.0, "xTo": 0.0, "yTo": 70.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為所有......從這片泥濘的土地上爬起來的人們。", "name": "葦草"}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小小的花朵飄搖落下，跌進沼澤，無聲地枯敗在爛泥之中。"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}